OL,3,CMultiple injuries as car strikes
OL,4,Cpedestrians, man arrested
OL,6,FA man has been arrested after a car
OL,7,Fhit and injured pedestrians in Derby
OL,8,Fon Saturday night.
OL,10,FSeveral people were injured, some of
OL,11,Fthem seriously, in the incident in the
OL,12,Fcity centre, according to Derbyshire
OL,13,FPolice. They were treated at the scene
OL,14,Fbefore being taken to hospital.
OL,16,FPolice said the car believed to be
OL,17,Finvolved was stopped after the
OL,18,Fincident in Friar Gate at about 9.30pm.
OL,20,FThe driver, a man in his 30s, was
OL,21,Farrested and is in police custody.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
