OL,4,Cpedestrians, man arrested
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FA section of Friar Gate is expected to
OL,12,Fbe closed for some time and people are
OL,13,Fasked to avoid the area.
OL,15,FPolice have asked anyone who saw a
OL,16,Fblack Suzuki Swift in Derby around the
OL,17,Ftime of the incident to get in touch.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
