OL,3,CMultiple injuries as car strikes
OL,4,Cpedestrians, man arrested
OL,6,FThe force's statement said: "Although
OL,7,Fwe know this will be alarming, we
OL,8,Fwould like to reassure people that we
OL,9,Fdo not believe there is an ongoing
OL,10,Frisk to the public."
OL,12,FDerby North MP Catherine Atkinson said
OL,13,Fshe was "deeply shocked" by reports of
OL,14,Fthe casualties.
OL,16,FPosting on Facebook, she said: "My
OL,17,Fthoughts are with those injured and
OL,18,FI'm grateful to our emergency services.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
