OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774768381
OL,3,CMultiple injuries as car strikes
OL,4,Cpedestrians, man arrested
OL,6,F"Please follow police advice and avoid
OL,7,Fthe area. Anyone who has information
OL,8,Fshould contact them as soon as
OL,9,Fpossible."
OL,11,FBaggy Shanker, the MP for Derby South,
OL,12,Fsaid his thoughts were with "everyone
OL,13,Fwho has been affected and with their
OL,14,Floved ones".
